%h1 Question: minVal()
%p
  Write a method called
  %code minVal()
  that takes an array of
  %code int
  values as a parameter and returns the smallest value in the array.

%pre{ lang: 'text/x-java' }
  :preserve
    public static int minVal(int[] y)
    {
        int bestSoFar = y[0];
        for (int i = 1; i &lt;= y.length; i++)
        {
            if (y[i] &lt; bestSoFar)
            {
                bestSoFar = i;
            }
        }

        return bestSoFar;
    }
    </pre>

